# Design and code quality

**UI / frontend work:**
- Read `/docs/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md` or project-root `DESIGN.md` before building UI (Impeccable uses `DESIGN.md`)
- Invoke **Impeccable** skill for design, polish, audit, live browser iteration
- No default blue buttons, grey cards, system font stacks, or generic AI layout

**All code:**
- **Ponytail** rule applies (YAGNI, stdlib first, minimal diff)
- No unrequested abstractions, dependencies, or boilerplate
